Class EventAtomicSource

  • java.lang.Object
    • fr.sorbonne_u.devs_simulation.models.events.EventSource
      • fr.sorbonne_u.devs_simulation.models.events.EventAtomicSource
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class EventAtomicSource
extends EventSource
    The class AtomicEventSource implements a description of an atomic model as event source but perhaps profoundly inserted in a composite model that may converter the event from the source type to another in the sink type.
